&lt;li&gt;Proficient in photography and videography&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in Canva, Premiere Pro, and CapCut (or similar tools)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient across Instagram, LinkedIn, Facebook &amp;amp; YouTube Strong copywriting ability with excellent English &amp;amp; Swahili communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
